HEADWORD: Preciosity
<hw>Pre`ci*os"i*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Preciousness;
something precious.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Sir T.
Browne.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
